title: ub40 rehearsels 2008 rar
description:
UB40 Rehearsals Session 2008
This is the audio taken from a rehearsals session that UB40 did on May 6th 2008 at their studios in Birmingham, the session was arranged for a group of fans to welcome new lead singer Duncan Campbell and new keyboard player Tony Mullins to the band. Also there was Maxi priest who performs a few songs with UB40 and who will be joining them on their new tour.
ENJOY!!
